// AliasChip
// Pill-shaped chip displaying a single alias string with an optional remove (×)
// button. Used within AliasEditor to list existing aliases.

FUNCTION AliasChip(alias, onRemove, disabled) -> JSX                   EXPORT
  Renders the alias text inside a rounded pill.
  IF onRemove is provided: renders a × button that calls onRemove.
  Button is disabled (with reduced opacity) when disabled prop is true.
